<div class="home-container">
  <div id="home-title">
    <h1 class="home-h1 mb-5">Photograph<span class="green-point">R.</span></h1>
  </div>
  <div id="home-content">
    <h2 class="home-h2">Libérez votre temps,<br>photographiez plus !</h2>
    <div id="home-links">
      <% if user_signed_in?  %>
        <%= link_to "C'est parti !", tasks_path, class: 'btn-connect' %>
        <%= link_to 'Faire un essai', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn-tester' %>
      <% else  %>
        <%= link_to 'Se Connecter', user_session_path, class: 'btn-connect' %>
        <%= link_to 'Faire un essai', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn-tester' %>
      <% end  %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="icon-scroll-down pulsate-fwd">
    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down mb-5"></i>
  </div>

  <div class="home-section mt-5 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
    <div class="example-text p-5">
      <i class="fas fa-thumbtack m-3 icon-gray-home px-3"></i>
      <h3>Une vue globale de toutes vos tâches<span class="green-point">.</span></h3>
    </div>
    <div class="example-image-shadow">
      <%= image_tag 'example-photographr-02.png', width: 800 %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="home-section home-section-white d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center pt-5 pb-5">
    <div class="example-image-shadow">
      <%= image_tag 'example-photographr-05.png', width: 800 %>
    </div>
    <div class="example-text p-5">
      <i class="fas fa-magic m-3 p-3 icon-gray-home"></i>
      <h3>Un worflow automatisé<span class="green-point">.</span></h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="home-section d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
    <div class="example-text p-5">
      <i class="fas fa-users m-3 py-3 icon-gray-home"></i>
      <h3>Toutes les informations clients centralisées<span class="green-point">.</span></h3>
    </div>
    <div class="example-image-shadow">
      <%= image_tag 'example-photographr-04.png', width: 800 %>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="home-section home-section-white d-flex justify-content-center align-items-start">
    <div class="box-testimonial d-flex flex-column align-items-center pl-3 pr-3 ml-5 mr-5">
      <%= image_tag 'photographe-1.jpg', class: "avatar-home" %>
      <h4 class='text-center mb-3 mt-4'>Juliette Ménard</h4>
      <p class="text-left"><i class="fas fa-quote-left pr-2"></i>Outil utile, pratique, simple d’utilisation et très complet pour mon utilisation quotidienne. Je ne saurai déjà plus m’en passer ! Et surtout, quel gain de temps !</p>
    </div>
    <div class="box-testimonial d-flex flex-column align-items-center pl-3 pr-3 ml-5 mr-5">
      <%= image_tag 'photographe-2.jpg', class: "avatar-home" %>
      <h4 class='text-center mb-3 mt-4'>Erwan Girard</h4>
      <p class="text-left"><i class="fas fa-quote-left pr-2"></i>La solution que l’on attendait pour la gestion client, outil pratique et indispensable au photographe. J’apprécie le temps gagné, dans la mise en place de workflow et planning. Merci Photographr !</p>
    </div>
    <div class="box-testimonial d-flex flex-column align-items-center pl-3 pr-3 ml-5 mr-5">
      <%= image_tag 'photographe-3.jpg', class: "avatar-home" %>
      <h4 class='text-center mb-3 mt-4'>Luce Riou</h4>
      <p class="text-left"><i class="fas fa-quote-left pr-2"></i>Ce site est très bien conçu et réalisé, il permet une gestion efficace et conviviale de son activité de photographe. L’essayer c’est l’adopter.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="home-end-container">
    <div class="home-h2-container ml-5">
      <h2 class="home-h2 home-h2-white ml-5">À votre tour !</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="home-links-end">
      <% if user_signed_in?  %>
        <%= link_to "C'est parti !", tasks_path, class: 'btn-connect btn-white' %>
        <%= link_to 'Faire un essai', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn-tester' %>
      <% else  %>
        <%= link_to 'Se Connecter', user_session_path, class: 'btn-connect btn-white' %>
        <%= link_to 'Faire un essai', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn-tester' %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer d-flex justify-content-around align-items-center">
    <div class="icone-white">
      <i class="fab fa-facebook mr-4"></i><i class="fab fa-instagram mr-4"></i><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
    </div>
    <p>Made with<i class="fas fa-heart ml-1 mr-1"></i>by the photographR team.</p>
  </div>

</div>
